Dry shampoo must !!!!! Before you’re doing your makeup spray your dry shampoo into your hair, AND LEAVE IT !! Don’t blend it in or brush it out. Let it sit and soak up the oils. Once you’re done with your makeup THEN go in and blend that out. If you find there to be a cast or hard to blend area hit it with a blow dryer for like a minute it’ll take that away! Works SOOO much more effectively than spray and blending it. On every can it says to leave it for 3-5 minutes and we all out here just doing it all wrong!
